{"tid":722859,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣可以睇第一次就get到曬MOS係講緊耶穌","createTime":"2018-06-30T02:20:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T04:02:20.000Z","uid":74778,"like":34,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"dc6b71cef1b58edf594d700f09c588819e90cf5a","tid":722859,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T02:20:23.000Z","msg":"係Nefix已經睇左唔知幾多次，但係每一次都發現新既位置，睇到個編劇同d對白既用心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我第一次睇都唔覺，只係覺得好噚氣，好似龍珠咁飛天盲打，睇唔明。<br />\n<br />\n近排翻睇返就一下就睇出<br />\n<br />\n尤其係一開始已經話 送自己唯一既兒子去地球既時候，同埋佢地係地球太空船上重遇，佢生父提佢 人類會誤解佢，要佢帶比人類希望<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/082720_2bb35896ddbdb867990d68953b6101c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F082720_2bb35896ddbdb867990d68953b6101c4.png&h=dcbb6c25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電影中都強調，Kal el 係氪星幾世紀以黎唯一一個唔帶有任何目的地自然生產既嬰兒，代表自由，<br />\n<br />\n自由係聖經中有好重要既位置，阿當夏娃因為上帝賦予自由意志而<strong>&rdquo;選擇犯罪&rdquo;</strong>食禁果，從此人類有原罪。直到耶穌出現，犧牲自己代人贖罪，人類重獲自由, 係選擇同犯罪入面，罪已經被贖，人從始就有無比自由。<br />\n<br />\n而係好幾段ZOD既對話入面都睇到，佢係一個無自由既人，佢既生存係為左保護自己既族人，為左征服侵略其他有價值同適合自己族人既生存既星球。<br />\n<br />\n<em>其實就同阿當夏娃食知善惡樹既果實，得到分辨是非既道德觀之前(動物狀態)一樣，無話乜野係好同壞，只有生存既概念一樣。<br />\n</em><br />\n<br />\n直到，氪星上唯一一個自由誕生既人，先終止左<strong>無自由價值既生命</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WRt_UVxgQZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWRt_UVxgQZk&d=xYDnsYMJANfNLmNsctYieTACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=37ace931\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WRt_UVxgQZk</a><br />\n<br />\n另外有個唔起眼既角色，ZOD條𡃁，佢同Superman 打果陣有口嗡嗡講左幾句野，<strong>&rdquo;你雖然有道德觀念，不過，歷史已經話比你聽，進化永遠會勝利&rdquo;</strong><br />\n<br />\n<em>佢提出既反思係道德同進化既矛盾。如果人係只係為左生存，就好似ZOD咁，生存意義就為左存活，而為左存活得更好，就要進化，變得更強壯更聰明(求生技能上)<br />\n但係Clark就唔係，佢係人類圈子長大，有人類既道德，從小就會從意外中救人，幫助弱小，有善惡觀念，都可以話<strong>Clark既生存意義係向善(耶穌)，而佢生父 Jor el 就話比佢聽佢既生存意義，係地球生存既意義，就係&rdquo;<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">成為兩族人之間既橋樑，必要時要領導人類走出困境，成為人類既領袖。(you can be the bridge between two people) </span>&rdquo;</strong></em><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zWTbLZCR84k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzWTbLZCR84k&d=xYDnsYMJANfNLmNsctYieTACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=bd0415a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zWTbLZCR84k</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Y65rBJ6wbXg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FY65rBJ6wbXg&d=xYDnsYMJANfNLmNsctYieTACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=88a541ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Y65rBJ6wbXg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMOS用既係插敘，唔只係講故事，欣賞既角度係電影畫面以外導演想表達既意義，係神既誕生，係一個救世主既內心掙扎。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/174437_02a0ec9d80440567b93adca01d06d350.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F174437_02a0ec9d80440567b93adca01d06d350.png&h=7fcfc0fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/174438_51b1b3d8aba787b1ead8c0afc074c271.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F174438_51b1b3d8aba787b1ead8c0afc074c271.gif&h=39b39350&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88a8fe47ffd4d1f240291cd98b9225dfa09df213","tid":722859,"uid":14497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T02:32:23.000Z","msg":"真正的神誕生了"},{"pid":"2151b1460c74a58fae010eb59befa46817eb3fd1","tid":722859,"uid":124450,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"88a8fe47ffd4d1f240291cd98b9225dfa09df213","tid":722859,"uid":14497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T02:32:23.000Z","msg":"真正的神誕生了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T02:35:08.000Z","msg":"但他仍會講粗口"},{"pid":"0bb7016bd7f0ec410e5b76bd7397860e3bc